# Jutge Wrapped Guidance

- Read `CONTRIBUTING.md` and `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` before making structural changes.
- Put slide UI in `src/features/wrapped/slides/*`, wrapped business logic in `src/features/wrapped/*`, and app-wide state changes in `src/context/*` or `src/App.tsx`.
- Keep `src/components/*` generic unless a component is intentionally wrapped-specific.
- Do not hand-edit generated clients in `src/api/jutgeClient.ts` or `jutge_api_client.ts` unless the change is an intentional sync/regeneration.
- Update `src/i18n/locales/en.json`, `src/i18n/locales/es.json`, and `src/i18n/locales/ca.json` together when UI copy changes.
- Do not commit `.env` files, secrets, or anything under `artifacts/`.
- Before finishing substantial work, run `npm run lint`, `npm run test`, and `npm run build`.
